{% block content %}

	<div class="container py-24 text-center ">

		<div class="relative after:absolute after:top-1/2 after:left-0 after:w-full after:h-[1px] after:bg-gray-200 mb-8">
			<h2 class="relative z-10 inline-block px-6 mx-auto mb-0 bg-white">Introducing the Eye Guide MC</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto copy">

			<p class="font-semibold">The Eye Guide MC is a new device invented by a person with Parkinson's, for people with Parkinson's. It is a simple,
			wearable aid that can drastically improve the quality of life of a person with Parkinson's Disease.</p>
			
			<p>The device sits discreetly over the wearer's ear, lining up to their visual field. It provides a visual sensory stimulus
			which can help to improve a person with Parkinson's balance, walking and tremor.</p>

		</div>

		<a href="{{site.url}}/about-eyeguide-mc" class="mt-8 btn btn--tertiary">About the Eye Guide MC</a>
		
	</div>


	<div class="p-4 md:mt-12 bg-primary">

		<div class="container flex flex-wrap p-0 md:transform md:-translate-y-1/2 max-w-screen-3xl">

			<div class="w-full p-2 sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/4 lg:p-4">
				<div class="w-full p-4 bg-white drop-shadow-2xl lg:p-8">
					<p class="mb-0 h4">No surgery</p>
					<p>No surgery required - just a simple fitting by our experts</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="w-full p-2 sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/4 lg:p-4">
				<div class="w-full p-4 bg-white drop-shadow-2xl lg:p-8">
					<p class="mb-0 h4">No surgery</p>
					<p>No surgery required - just a simple fitting by our experts</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="w-full p-2 sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/4 lg:p-4">
				<div class="w-full p-4 bg-white drop-shadow-2xl lg:p-8">
					<p class="mb-0 h4">No surgery</p>
					<p>No surgery required - just a simple fitting by our experts</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="w-full p-2 sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/4 lg:p-4">
				<div class="w-full p-4 bg-white drop-shadow-2xl lg:p-8">
					<p class="mb-0 h4">No surgery</p>
					<p>No surgery required - just a simple fitting by our experts</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>


		<div class="container flex-wrap items-start mt-8 text-white max-w-screen-3xl lg:flex">

			<div class="lg:w-3/5 xl:w-3/4">

				<h2 class="inline-block relative after:absolute after:bg-tertiary after:w-full after:h-[2px] after:bottom-0 after:left-0 mb-8">How it works</h2>

				<ul class="mb-8 lg:w-4/5">

					<li class="relative py-4 pl-6 before:rounded-full before:absolute before:top-6 before:left-0 before:bg-tertiary before:w-2 before:h-2">The Eye Guide MC is a simple device that can instantly improve the debilitating symptoms of Parkinson's Disease (speech,
					tremor, movement, coordination).</li>
					
					<li class="relative py-4 pl-6 before:rounded-full before:absolute before:top-6 before:left-0 before:bg-tertiary before:w-2 before:h-2">The Eye Guide MC is worn over the ear, pointing out along the eye line and sites along the meridian line.</li>
					
					<li class="relative py-4 pl-6 before:rounded-full before:absolute before:top-6 before:left-0 before:bg-tertiary before:w-2 before:h-2">The Guide sits in the peripheral vision, so that the eye only sees the very tip of it.</li>

					<li class="relative py-4 pl-6 before:rounded-full before:absolute before:top-6 before:left-0 before:bg-tertiary before:w-2 before:h-2">This enables the brain to work with the eye, giving new signals to the Basal Ganglia, the part of the brain that
					controls movement.</li>
				
				</ul>

				<div class="mx-auto text-center lg:text-left lg:m-0">

					{% include "_components/phone-number.twig" with {
						classes: 'btn btn--outline-secondary',
						calltag: true,
					} %}
					
					<span class="block p-2 font-semibold md:inline-block">or</span>

					<a class="btn btn--secondary" href="{{site.url}}/contact">Book a free consultation</a>

				</div>

			</div>

			<div class="flex flex-wrap mt-8 -mx-4 lg:mt-0 lg:mx-0 lg:w-2/5 xl:w-1/4">

				<div class="w-1/2 p-4 lg:w-full lg:mb-8">
					<img class="object-cover object-center w-full" src="https://placedog.net/500" alt="">
				</div>

				<div class="w-1/2 p-4 lg:w-full">
					<img class="object-cover object-center w-full" src="https://placedog.net/500" alt="">
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

		<div class="flex flex-wrap mx-auto mb-16 lg:mt-16 max-w-screen-3xl text-tertiary-light">

			<div class="w-full p-4 sm:w-1/2">
				<div class="h-full p-8 text-white bg-primary-light copy">
					
					<h3 class="relative mb-6 inline-block after:absolute after:left-0 after:bottom-[-5px] after:h-[1px] after:w-full after:bg-primary-lightest">Driven to help people with Parkinson’s</h3>

					<p class="font-semibold">Eye Guide MC was created by a person with Parkinson’s, for people with Parkinson’s. Every Parkinson’s person is welcome
					to talk to us about a fitting.</p>

					<p>The device was born out of a very personal Parkinson’s journey. Sandra, the inventor of Eye Guide MC, is in a unique
					position to understand the needs of people with Parkinson’s and her mission is to improve the lives of those with the
					condition. She persevered to create a device that will change lives for the better.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="w-full p-4 sm:w-1/2">
				<div class="h-full p-8 text-white bg-primary-light copy">
					
					<h3 class="relative mb-6 inline-block after:absolute after:left-0 after:bottom-[-5px] after:h-[1px] after:w-full after:bg-primary-lightest">Patients first</h3>

					<p class="font-semibold">Here at Eye Guide MC, patient care is our top priority. We're here to guide you through the full process of living with
					your new Eye Guide MC, from an initial consultation, to the fitting, to follow up advice. All of our highly trained team
					of technicians come from caring backgrounds and are trained by a Parkinson's Nurse Specialist.</p>

					<p>Our friendly staff will greet you at the door of our clinic and will be with you all the way to reclaiming your
					independence.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		
		</div>
		
	</div>

